	<h3>Why Digital Direct Democracy?</h3>
		<p>
			<table style="line-height: 150%;"><tr>
				<td style="text-align: justify;text-justify: newspaper;position: relative; top:-40px;">
				In a <a href='http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Democracy#Direct' target='_blank'>real democracy</a>, people decide themselves how to govern 
			        their country instead of relying on <a href='http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Particracy' target='_blank'>untrustworthy representatives</a>.
			        <a href='http://www.democratie-directe.be' target='_blank'>Our objective</a> is to bring <a href='http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Direct_democracy' target='_blank'> direct democracy</a> in Belgium, 
